Package: renovae
Title: An R Interface For The Novae Deep Learning Framework
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Gabriele", "Sales", , "gabriele.sales@unipd.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a demonstration interface to the 'novae' deep 
    learning framework. This package serves as a proof-of-concept wrapper, 
    enabling basic model initialization and interaction within the R 
    environment via 'reticulate'. It is intended for experimental use and 
    to illustrate the integration of 'novae' architectures with R 
    workflows.
